snippet.title: Rail Rampage C64 | early trailer
snippet.description:
Finally ready to post some kinda trailer for this. I'm super happy with the results so far and I hope you enjoy it when it releases! The full game will feature several levels, a built in level editor and hopefully an original OST.
See you then! :3

MUSIC: Minipitt by Goto80:
